Please read the few steps below to install the plugin and get everything working.

1) Upload the 'comment-image-uploader' folder to the plugins directory: /wp-content/plugins/

2) Activate the plugin via the WordPress admin dashboard

3) Open comments.php of your current theme and insert the following code
   wherever you want the image upload option to appear.

<?php if (function_exists('upload_comment_images')) upload_comment_images(); ?>
